==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Engorged
<hw>En*gorged"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>p. a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Swallowed with greediness, or in large draughts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Filled to excess with blood or
other liquid; congested.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Engorgement</ent>⟦br⟧
